{
  "info": {
    "_postman_id": "a9004add-321a-4c1f-a8a9-90c84ccfaa50",
    "name": "Sales Monitoring — Flip Disbursement",
    "description": "Koleksi lengkap API testing untuk project Sales Monitoring dengan integrasi Flip for Business.\n\n## Setup\n1. Import collection ini ke Postman\n2. Buat Environment baru dengan variabel berikut:\n   - `base_url` → `http://localhost:8000/api`\n   - `token` → (kosong, akan terisi otomatis setelah login)\n   - `admin_token` → (kosong, akan terisi otomatis setelah login admin)\n   - `sales_token` → (kosong, akan terisi otomatis setelah login sales)\n\n## Alur Testing\n1. Auth → Register / Login\n2. Admin: Kelola produk, pelanggan, target\n3. Sales: Input transaksi\n4. Admin: Generate & disburse komisi\n5. Webhook: Simulasi callback Flip",
    "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json",
    "_exporter_id": "24787861"
  },
  "item": [
    {
      "name": "🔐 Auth",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "Register",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "if (pm.response.code === 201 || pm.response.code === 200) {",
                  "    const res = pm.response.json();",
                  "    if (res.token) pm.collectionVariables.set('token', res.token);",
                  "    pm.test('Register berhasil', () => pm.response.to.have.status(201));",
                  "} else {",
                  "    pm.test('Register response: ' + pm.response.code, () => {});",
                  "}"
                ],
                "type": "text/javascript",
                "packages": {},
                "requests": {}
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "Accept",
                "value": "application/json"
              }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n    \"nama\": \"Admin Test\",\n    \"email\": \"admin@test.com\",\n    \"password\": \"password123\",\n    \"password_confirmation\": \"password123\",\n    \"role\": \"admin\"\n}",
